snippet.title: PAPRIUM - RULE, BE RULED, OR DIE!
snippet.description:
Pre-order now on http://paprium.com
PAPRIUM is a new 16-Bit, post-apocalyptic, outrageous brawler game. PAPRIUM is the biggest Mega Drive / SEGA Genesis game ever made and features multiple game modes, 24 Levels and up to 5 Selectable Characters!

This is a brand new AAA Mega Drive / SEGA Genesis game, developed from the ground up, to be released in 2017! It has been crafted at WM's Magical Game Factory through the Investor's votes, thousands of suggestions and a team driven by true passion and 16-Bit excellence.

More informations and preorder details available at:
http://www.paprium.com
http://www.magicalgamefactory.com

Audio Credits:
First Track «DECAPITATOR» by Zebre-Rouge
https://soundcloud.com/zebre-rouge/

Second Track PAPRIUM game's «Asian Chill» by David Burton & Trevin Hughes
https://soundcloud.com/groovemaster303/paprium-music-sampler-v2

Music Mixing & Sound Design by Manels Favre
